# Chapter 5 — Testing

---

## 5.1 Testing Approach

ALM 4.0 is tested across three levels:

| Level | Type | Purpose |
|---|---|---|
| Unit | Per-module function tests | Validate individual module outputs in isolation |
| Integration | Pipeline segment tests | Ensure correct data handoff between modules |
| System | End-to-end tests | Validate full pipeline output for known audio samples |

---

## 5.2 Unit Test Cases

