| Test ID | Input | Expected Output | Result |
|---|---|---|---|
| UT-01 | Silent WAV file | `audio` array of zeros, `sr = 16000` | ✅ Pass |
| UT-02 | Stereo MP3 | Converted to mono; `audio.ndim == 1` | ✅ Pass |
| UT-03 | Non-16kHz audio | Resampled to `sr = 16000` | ✅ Pass |
| UT-04 | Clipped audio (peak > 1.0) | Normalised: `max(abs(audio)) == 1.0` | ✅ Pass |

